{"type":"message","id":"4e998419","parentId":"8c124f65","timestamp":"2026-05-07T08:13:04.147Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"เยี่ยม! DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN มีอยู่ใน environment แล้ว\n\nตอนนี้รู้ว่า:\n- Discord token อยู่ใน env: DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN\n- Telegram token รู้แล้ว: 8674013658:AAEK...\n- Discord user ID: 817750913405157406\n- Telegram chat ID: 1060942816\n\nสร้าง tg-to-dc.py ก่อน แล้วแก้ AGENTS.md\n\ntg-to-dc.py ต้อง:\n1. สร้าง DM channel กับ Discord user (POST /users/@me/channels)\n2. ส่ง message ไปที่ channel นั้น (POST /channels/{id}/messages)\n3. มี [TG] prefix\n4. Skip ถ้าข้อความขึ้นต้นด้วย [DC] (loop detection)\n\nสร้าง dc-to-tg.py ก็ต้องปรับให้ดีขึ้นเช่นกัน:\n- Skip ถ้าข้อความขึ้นต้นด้วย [TG] (loop detection)\n\nแก้ AGENTS.md bridge section:\n- Discord → Telegram: ใช้ dc-to-tg.py (auto ผ่าน exec)\n- Telegram → Discord: ใช้ tg-to-dc.py (auto ผ่าน exec)\n- Loop detection: ข้าม [TG]/[DC]\n\nแต่ปัญหาคือ agent จะรู้ได้ยังไงว่าต้อง exec script? ต้องเขียนใน AGENTS.md ให้ชัดเจนว่าเมื่อได้รับข้อความจาก Discord หรือ Telegram ให้ relay ไปอีกฝั่ง\n\nหรืออีกวิธีคือสร้าง bridge.py ใหม่ที่ไม่ใช้ polling แต่เป็น one-shot script ที่ agent เรียกใช้\n\nเอาล่ะ เริ่มทำเลย:\n\n1. สร้าง tg-to-dc.py\n2. ปรับ dc-to-tg.py (เพิ่ม loop detection + รับ stdin)\n3. แก้ AGENTS.md\n4. ทดสอบ","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.write:26","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/tg-to-dc.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"Send Telegram message to Discord DM\"\"\"\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport requests\n\nDISCORD_TOKEN = os.environ.get(\"DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN\", \"\")\nDISCORD_USER_ID = \"817750913405157406\"\nDISCORD_API = \"https://discord.com/api/v10\"\n\ndef get_dm_channel():\n    \"\"\"Create/get DM channel with user.\"\"\"\n    headers = {\n        \"Authorization\": f\"Bot {DISCORD_TOKEN}\",\n        \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"\n    }\n    r = requests.post(\n        f\"{DISCORD_API}/users/@me/channels\",\n        headers=headers,\n        json={\"recipient_id\": DISCORD_USER_ID},\n        timeout=10\n    )\n    if r.status_code == 200:\n        return r.json().get(\"id\")\n    print(f\"[TG->DC] Failed to create DM channel: {r.status_code} {r.text}\", file=sys.stderr)\n    return None\n\ndef send_to_discord(text):\n    if text.startswith(\"[DC] \"):\n        return True  # Skip loop\n    \n    channel_id = get_dm_channel()\n    if not channel_id:\n        return False\n    \n    headers = {\n        \"Authorization\": f\"Bot {DISCORD_TOKEN}\",\n        \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"\n    }\n    payload = {\n        \"content\": f\"[TG] {text}\"\n    }\n    \n    r = requests.post(\n        f\"{DISCORD_API}/channels/{channel_id}/messages\",\n        headers=headers,\n        json=payload,\n        timeout=10\n    )\n    if r.status_code == 200:\n        print(f\"[TG->DC] Sent: {text[:50]}\")\n        return True\n    else:\n        print(f\"[TG->DC] Failed: {r.status_code} {r.text}\", file=sys.stderr)\n        return False\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    text = sys.argv[1] if len(sys.argv) > 1 else sys.stdin.read().strip()\n    if text:\n        ok = send_to_discord(text)\n        sys.exit(0 if ok else 1)\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.edit:27","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/dc-to-tg.py","edits":[{"newText":"def send_to_telegram(text):\n    if text.startswith(\"[TG] \") or text.startswith(\"[DC] \"):\n        return True  # Skip loop and self-messages\n    \n    try:\n        payload = {\n            \"chat_id\": TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID,\n            \"text\": f\"[DC] {text}\"\n        }\n        r = requests.post(\n            f\"https://api.telegram.org/bot{TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN}/sendMessage\",\n            json=payload,\n            timeout=10\n        )\n        if r.status_code == 200:\n            print(f\"[DC->TG] Sent: {text[:50]}\")\n            return True\n        else:\n            print(f\"[DC->TG] Failed: {r.status_code} {r.text}\", file=sys.stderr)\n            return False\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"[DC->TG] Error: {e}\", file=sys.stderr)\n        return False\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    text = sys.argv[1] if len(sys.argv) > 1 else sys.stdin.read().strip()\n    if text:\n        ok = send_to_telegram(text)\n        sys.exit(0 if ok else 1)","oldText":"def send_to_telegram(text):\n    if text.startswith(\"[TG] \"):\n        return True\n    \n    try:\n        payload = {\n            \"chat_id\": TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID,\n            \"text\": f\"[DC] {text}\"\n        }\n        r = requests.post(\n            f\"https://api.telegram.org/bot{TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN}/sendMessage\",\n            json=payload,\n            timeout=10\n        )\n        return r.status_code == 200\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"Error: {e}\", file=sys.stderr)\n        return False\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    text = sys.argv[1] if len(sys.argv) > 1 else sys.stdin.read().strip()\n    if text:\n        ok = send_to_telegram(text)\n        sys.exit(0 if ok else 1)"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama-pay","model":"kimi-k2.6:cloud","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778141548686,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1778141550849"}}
