{"type":"message","id":"6d82d477","parentId":"92c3a6b5","timestamp":"2026-05-07T08:38:16.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说 Discord 还没同步。我刚创建了一个基于 HTTP polling 的 Discord 监听器，不需要 websocket 库。\n\n让我启动它在后台，然后测试 Discord -> Telegram 是否自动工作。\n\n然后我需要告诉用户：\n1. Discord -> Telegram 现在会自动运行（通过后台 daemon）\n2. Telegram -> Discord 需要我每次手动转发（因为 Telegram 方向由 agent 处理）\n\n但我应该先启动 daemon。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.exec:44","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && nohup python3 bridge-dc-listener.py > bridge-dc.log 2>&1 &\necho \"PID: $!\"\nsleep 2\ncat bridge-dc.log 2>/dev/null | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama-pay","model":"kimi-k2.6:cloud","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778143091311,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1778143093264"}}
