{"type":"message","id":"e0444a11","parentId":"9edeaea2","timestamp":"2026-05-07T08:44:23.093Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bridge-dc-listener.py 正在工作了！它抓到了 Discord 的消息并转发到了 Telegram。\n\n现在问题是：它转发了所有历史消息（包括之前的）。这会导致重复发送。我需要：\n1. 告诉用户 Discord -> Telegram 现在自动工作了\n2. 让用户在 Discord 发一条测试消息确认实时转发\n3. 对于 Telegram -> Discord，我作为 agent 仍然需要每次手动调用 tg-to-dc.py\n\n但等等，看看日志，它发送了：\n- \"ทำไม discord มันดูช้า กว่า เทเรแกรม\"\n- \"กูอยากให้ตอบไปทั้ง telegram และ discord ลิ้งกันเล\"\n- \"แบบ2\"\n- \"Telegram ทักไปไม่ยอมตอบ\"\n\n这些消息应该已经在 Telegram 了（因为之前转发过）。bridge 现在又在重复发送。\n\n问题：第一次启动时，last_msg_id 是 None，所以它获取最近的 10 条消息并全部转发。这在第一次启动时会导致重复。\n\n我需要在脚本里加逻辑：第一次启动时不转发历史消息，只转发新消息。或者，保存 last_msg_id 到文件。\n\n让我修复这个问题，以避免每次重启都重复转发历史消息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.edit:72","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/bridge-dc-listener.py","edits":[{"newText":"    last_msg_id = None\n    state_file = \"/home/apinan/.openclaw/workspace/bridge-dc-state.json\"\n    if os.path.exists(state_file):\n        try:\n            with open(state_file) as f:\n                saved = json.load(f)\n                last_msg_id = saved.get(\"last_msg_id\")\n                print(f\"[Bridge] Resumed from state, last_msg_id={last_msg_id}\")\n        except Exception:\n            pass\n\n    # On first run, fetch latest message ID but don't relay history\n    if last_msg_id is None:\n        headers = {\"Authorization\": f\"Bot {DISCORD_TOKEN}\"}\n        r = requests.get(f\"{DISCORD_API}/channels/{channel_id}/messages?limit=1\", headers=headers, timeout=10)\n        if r.status_code == 200:\n            msgs = r.json()\n            if msgs:\n                last_msg_id = msgs[0].get(\"id\")\n                print(f\"[Bridge] First run, synced to latest message id={last_msg_id}\")\n\n    print(\"[Bridge] Polling started (Ctrl+C to stop)\")\n\n    while True:","oldText":"    last_msg_id = None\n    print(\